						display: block;
						font-size: 1.3rem;
						color: #fff;
						letter-spacing: normal;
						margin-bottom: 15px;
					}
					strong {
						color: #f2b43f;
						border-bottom: 1px solid #f2b43f;
						margin-left: 2px;
					}
				}
			}
		}
	}
